[0.000, "o", "ands: `init`, `add`, `rm`, `status`, `commit -m`, `log`, `show`,\r\u001b[5C\u001b[1B\u001b[2m  7 \u001b[22m`diff`, `checkout`, and `reset`.\r\u001b[5C\u001b[1B\u001b[2m  8 \u001b[22m\u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[5C\u001b[1B\u001b[38;2;248;248;242m\u001b[2m  9 \u001b[22mAll state lives on disk under `.minigit/`:\r\u001b[5C\u001b[1B\u001b[2m 10 \u001b[22m- `objects/<hash>` — raw file bytes, content-addressed with FNV-1a (64-bit, 16 hex\r\u001b[1B\u001b[39m \u001b[3G   \u001b[38;2;153;153;153m… +116 lines \u001b[39m\u001b[K\u001b[30;1H\u001b[28;3H"]
