[0.001, "o", "\u001b[1mmissing capability\u001b[22m: no wall-clock\u001b[67Gtime\u001b[72G(std\u001b[77Ghas\u001b[81Gonly\u001b[86Gmonotonic\u001b[96G\u001b[38;2;177;185;249mInstant\u001b[39m;\u001b[105G\u001b[38;2;177;185;249mtime\u001b[110G\u001b[39mmodule\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bunimplemented).\u001b[19GWorked\u001b[26Garound\u001b[33Gvia\u001b[37G\u001b[38;2;177;185;249mos.execute(\"date\",\"+%s\")\u001b[39m.\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[1mPlease submit these three upstream\u001b[38G\u001b[22mat\u001b[41Ghttps://github.com/promise-language/promise/issues\u001b[92G(each\u001b[98Ghas\u001b[102Gthe\u001b[106Gfiling\u001b[113Gheader).\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[1mBiggest surprise\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[22m\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1BThe bundled \u001b[38;2;177;185;249mpromise guide\u001b[39m is wrong about ownership: it says\u001b[64G plain \u001b[38;2;177;185;249mT\u001b[39m param\u001b[79Gter is a borrow, but a plain \u001b[38;2;177;185;249mstring\u001b[115G\u001b[39mpa\u001b[118Gam\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bactually \u001b[1mmoves the argument at the call site\u001b[48G\u001b[22mwhile\u001b[54Gbehaving as a non-movable borrow inside the callee. The real borrow\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bform is \u001b[38;2;177;185;249mstring&\u001b[39m.\u001b[20GT\u001b[22Gat m\u001b[27Gsmatch cost the most time. Also noted (in SUMMARY,\u001b[78Gnot filed): \u001b[38;2;"]
